des:
Listen to Daily Hukamnama Katha from Manji Sahib Diwan Hall, Sri Amritsar. 

To start, just say "Alexa, open hukamnama katha" or "Alexa, start hukamnama katha". At anytime, you can stop the radio by saying "Alexa, stop"

Disclaimer: The skill content is in Punjabi.
